, i.e.,\n$\\sim \\pi/2$ or $-\\pi/2$. The preliminary results from NO$\\nu$A favouring\nNormal Ordering and $\\delta$ near $-\\pi/2$ imply quasi-degenerate neutrino\nmasses in this model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Aug 2015 17:26:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Mar 2016 11:03:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-04"}
