ains why most TDE candidates are fainter than\nexpected.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Aug 2015 20:04:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Aug 2016 19:01:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 13 Jan 2017 10:13:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-26"}
