 not find conformity effects of comparable amplitude on\nlarge scales in the simulations and we propose that gas needs to be pushed out\nof dark matter halos more efficiently at high redshifts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Aug 2015 20:08:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-14"}
